@startuml UC04_Sequence
title UC04: 浏览和搜索课程 - 顺序图

actor "学生" as Student
boundary "课程搜索页面" as SearchPage
control "课程控制器" as CourseCtrl
entity "外部数据库接口" as DBInterface
entity "Course" as Course

Student -> SearchPage : 输入筛选条件(名称, 教师等)
SearchPage -> CourseCtrl : searchCourses(criteria)
CourseCtrl -> DBInterface : syncIfNeeded()
DBInterface --> CourseCtrl : latestData
CourseCtrl -> Course : findMatches(criteria)
Course --> CourseCtrl : results
CourseCtrl --> SearchPage : 展示课程列表及其详情
SearchPage -> Student : 显示结果
@enduml
